  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/internet/\" rel=\"tag\">互联网络</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/04/19/google-trends-email-notifications/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/cdeb9871ef9bbb73f0d89bd899562b2a/200047733/QQ20140419-1.jpg\" style=\"width: 620px; height: 233px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div>如果想要了解某样事物在网路上的流行程度，你可以打开 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/googletrends\">Google 搜索趋势</a>看看它有多热门。但每次访问网站总还是有些麻烦，于是 Google 日前为这项服务新增了电邮订阅的功能。从现在起，只要开启相关选项，你的邮箱就会定期收到最热搜索、特定主题等内容的趋势通知了。好的，废话不多说，我们先去添加「Engadget 中国版」啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://insidesearch.blogspot.com/2014/04/the-hottest-topics-on-google-delivered.html\" target=\"_blank\">Inside Search</a></span>、<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://www.google.com/trends/subscriptions\" target=\"_blank\">Google Trends</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/04/19/google-trends-email-notifications/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20872103/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/04/19/google-trends-email-notifications/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
